data.description: Charming and Unique! This attractive well maintained home features a casual and versatile multi-level floor plan. Enter into the ceramic tile foyer leading to a welcoming updated kitchen that opens to the dining room, both with ~real~ hardwood floors. The nearby family room includes a warm wood burning fireplace, new wall to wall carpet, and access the sunny 3 season Florida Room with 4 sets of sliding glass doors. Great place for morning coffee! Just a few steps up from the entry foyer gleaming solid hardwoods continue into a separate living room with a large picture window overlooking a nicely landscaped yard. The next level up you'll find 4 well-spaced bedrooms and two full baths. The 4th loft style bedroom makes a great getaway room, studio, or teen suite! Important recent upgrades include the switch from oil to economical and very comfortable gas hot water baseboard heat. More savings and comfort with the upgraded double hung insulated glass windows with easy tilt in cleaning. Other quality upgrades include new 6 panel doors, electrical service panel, much fresh paint and beautiful refinished, solid hardwood floors throughout most of the house. The driveway was expanded for extra parking and the carport was rebuilt with more windows and left open to allow natural light into the kitchen and dining areas. The paver sidewalk accents the entry and the matching paver patio out back is ready for summer cookouts! You'll appreciate the low traffic cul-de-sac location and deep .25 acre lot. Grendon Farms is a small attractive community conveniently located and in the very popular Red Clay School district. Come spend some time and explore this terrific home!
